{"id":35898,"date":"2024-02-08T15:26:17","date_gmt":"2024-02-08T09:56:17","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=35898"},"modified":"2023-03-31T15:42:31","modified_gmt":"2023-03-31T10:12:31","slug":"cool-bedroom-ideas","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/cool-bedroom-ideas\/","title":{"rendered":"Cool Bedroom Ideas: 8 Budget-Friendly And Easy To Replicate Designs"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Try these cool bedroom ideas in your home to create a space that inspires and motivates.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Sometimes we come across homes, interiors or buildings that we can only describe as \u2018seriously cool\u2019 or \u2018mind-blowing\u2019 \u2014 because they leave us struggling for adjectives that would do justice. Such spaces inspire you to give your own home a makeover. So, let\u2019s start with the basics \u2014 the bedroom \u2014 the heart of your home. Here, we have listed some cool bedroom ideas that are easy to replicate in a budget-friendly way. Let\u2019s get started.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Cool Boys Bedroom Ideas For Those Who Love Adventure<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>While designing your kids\u2019 bedroom, consider including some fun activity elements. In this age of video games, it\u2019s become essential for your kids to be physically active, especially during their growing-up years. We have a great alternative if you are working parents and are uncomfortable letting your kids play outside unattended. For instance, in this kids\u2019 bedroom, we have created a room divider with pegs like you commonly see on mountain climbing walls. The divider works in three ways \u2014 a cool headboard, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-decor\/room-divider-ideas\/\">room divider<\/a> and indoor activity zone.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/08123123\/cool-boys-bedroom-idea.jpg\" alt=\"Cool boys bedroom idea with a room divider and indoor activity zone is essential for your kids to be physically active\" class=\"wp-image-35906\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/08123123\/cool-boys-bedroom-idea.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/08123123\/cool-boys-bedroom-idea-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/08123123\/cool-boys-bedroom-idea-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/08123123\/cool-boys-bedroom-idea-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Cool boys&#8217; bedroom ideas with an activity theme<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Make A Lasting Impression With Cool Bedroom Wall Designs<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>What makes a showstopper bedroom? The bed design, a unique wardrobe or a walk-in closet? Maybe an attractive vanity. We say the walls. It is the first thing you see in a bedroom. So, glam up the empty space above your bed. We fitted this bedroom with a marble and gold-lined wall behind the bed, making it the room\u2019s focal point. The gold-framed designer mirror perfectly completes the look of this stunning bedroom. It\u2019s also a great and unique way to use marble in your bedroom. If you are looking for a budget-friendly alternative, you can also use marble contact paper or a similar wallpaper.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/08123117\/cool-bedroom-wall-design.jpg\" alt=\"Cool bedroom wall design with marble and gold-lined, making it the room\u2019s focal point\" class=\"wp-image-35905\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/08123117\/cool-bedroom-wall-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/08123117\/cool-bedroom-wall-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/08123117\/cool-bedroom-wall-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/08123117\/cool-bedroom-wall-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Glam the space behind your bed with an accent wall<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Want to know what kind of bedroom designs suits you\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/02170353\/what-kind-of-bedroom-designs-suits-you.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Innovative Wall Installations Are Cool Bedroom Accessories<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Install some cool wall decor on the wall behind your bed to quickly transform the bedroom&#8217;s look. Instead of the usual picture frames, consider adding some decorative wall installations. It&#8217;s a hassle-free and interesting way of accessorising your room. In this bedroom, we installed a bunch of white birds to form a swirling pattern against the grey accent wall. For a budget-friendly alternative, you can also turn this into a weekend DIY project and create a similar installation with paper birds. We completed the look with a pair of copper pendant lights on either side of the bed.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/08123057\/cool-bedroom-accessories.jpg\" alt=\"A cool bedroom with wall decor on the wall transforms the bedroom's look\" class=\"wp-image-35901\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/08123057\/cool-bedroom-accessories.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/08123057\/cool-bedroom-accessories-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/08123057\/cool-bedroom-accessories-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/08123057\/cool-bedroom-accessories-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Cool bedroom accessories create a refreshing look<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Decorate Awkward Corners With Cool Floor Lamps For The Bedroom<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Every bedroom needs some extra attention to showcase your unique taste. A cool floor lamp can do the trick just right. For instance, in this bedroom, we placed a uniquely-shaped sleek floor lamp. It not only illuminates the room but also fills the empty corner beside the TV unit with a designer accessory.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/08123142\/decorate-awkward-corner-with-cool-floor-lamp-for-bedroom.jpg\" alt=\"A cool bedroom design with a uniquely-shaped sleek floor lamp illuminates the room\" class=\"wp-image-35909\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/08123142\/decorate-awkward-corner-with-cool-floor-lamp-for-bedroom.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/08123142\/decorate-awkward-corner-with-cool-floor-lamp-for-bedroom-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/08123142\/decorate-awkward-corner-with-cool-floor-lamp-for-bedroom-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/08123142\/decorate-awkward-corner-with-cool-floor-lamp-for-bedroom-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Up the oomph with cool floor lamps for the bedroom<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Cool Bedroom Themes Your Kids Will Love<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Display your kids\u2019 interests in their bedroom with theme-based <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/bedroom-design\/\">bedroom designs<\/a>. The best and easiest way to decorate a theme-based bedroom is to use cool bedroom wallpaper. For instance, in this bedroom, we used a peel-and-stick wallpaper on the entire wall behind the bed. The kid had astronaut ambitions so we used a brightly-hued cartoon-like space wallpaper to match their interests. The wallpaper\u2019s sea green colour looks perfect against the light-coloured wooden furniture.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/08123051\/astronaut-cool-bedroom-theme.jpg\" alt=\"Cool bedroom themed in astronaut style best and easiest way to decorate\" class=\"wp-image-35900\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/08123051\/astronaut-cool-bedroom-theme.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/08123051\/astronaut-cool-bedroom-theme-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/08123051\/astronaut-cool-bedroom-theme-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/08123051\/astronaut-cool-bedroom-theme-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Cool bedroom themes that reflect your kid\u2019s personality<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Cool Wall Decals For The Bedroom Ensure A Quick And Easy Makeover<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Wall decals and stickers are some of the most affordable decor items that can change the room\u2019s vibe completely in the blink of an eye. You can purchase cool wall decals for your bedrooms that match your interests and decorate the space. You can even engage your kids in a DIY project for a fun-filled weekend. Check out how this funky wall decal makes this kid&#8217;s bedroom stand out. The first thing that catches your eye when you enter the room is the decal. It looks stunning against the dark grey wall.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/08123136\/cool-wall-decals-for-bedroom.jpg\" alt=\"A cool bedroom idea with a funky wall decal makes the kid's bedroom stand out\" class=\"wp-image-35908\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/08123136\/cool-wall-decals-for-bedroom.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/08123136\/cool-wall-decals-for-bedroom-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/08123136\/cool-wall-decals-for-bedroom-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/08123136\/cool-wall-decals-for-bedroom-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Decals are budget-friendly room decoration ideas<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Want a bedroom that's modern and aesthetic\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/09145522\/want-a-bedroom-thats-modern-and-aesthetic.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Space-Saving And Cool Teenage Bedroom Ideas For Small Rooms<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Kids grow up rather quickly. And with every passing year, they keep collecting more items. So, investing in space-saving modular furniture is a brilliant idea. For instance, we used a multifunctional wardrobe in the kid&#8217;s bedroom here, which we customised with a seamless study desk. It can be pulled out and stowed away when not in use. No one will even guess it is there. Instead of side tables, we added built-in wall shelves to save more floor space. We also added a seating area by the window and a cool-looking curved chair.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/08123130\/cool-teen-bedroom-design-ideas.jpg\" alt=\"Cool teen bedroom design comes with space-saving modular furniture\" class=\"wp-image-35907\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/08123130\/cool-teen-bedroom-design-ideas.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/08123130\/cool-teen-bedroom-design-ideas-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/08123130\/cool-teen-bedroom-design-ideas-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/08123130\/cool-teen-bedroom-design-ideas-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A smart space-saving design for a teenager\u2019s bedroom<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Add Character With Cool Bedroom Ceiling Lights<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Nowadays, ceiling lights are much more than a functional bedroom staple. They have decorative value too. For instance, this gold artsy-looking chandelier captures your attention immediately in this <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/studio-apartment-interior-design-ideas\/\">studio apartment<\/a>. Another highlight of this apartment is the bookshelf that doubles up as an efficient room divider. It separates the living space from the sleeping area. It also comes with a revolving TV unit that can be moved 180\u00b0. Now you can watch your favourite shows from any side of the room!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/08123104\/cool-bedroom-ceiling-lights.jpg\" alt=\"Cool bedroom ceiling light adds dimension to your room\" class=\"wp-image-35902\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/08123104\/cool-bedroom-ceiling-lights.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/08123104\/cool-bedroom-ceiling-lights-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/08123104\/cool-bedroom-ceiling-lights-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/08123104\/cool-bedroom-ceiling-lights-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Decorative ceiling lights add dimension to your room<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>When it comes to decorating your or your kids&#8217; bedroom with a cool quotient, the choices are endless. Try these unique styles for cool bedroom ideas. If you still need help designing or revamping your bedroom, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/\">talk to our interior specialists<\/a>. Alternatively, you can check out our <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/\">blog section<\/a> for more bedroom design ideas.<\/p>\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Unwind In Your Personal Sanctuary<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get 20% extra space with modular interiors<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/>\n        <!-- <span class=\"sales-txt-label\" id=\"labeltxt\">Enter your name*<\/span>  -->\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"form-row dc-falg-row\">\n    